{"tid":2293112,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"周梓樂案 新聞片顯示有煙冒出  首認射TG入車場 警：不見煙","createTime":"2020-11-20T04:33:17.000Z","updateTime":"2020-11-20T11:25:39.000Z","uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":9,"uniUserReply":19,"replies":[{"pid":"deee7a9cea3f517111c6caa04c4cf052d1d81b7c","tid":2293112,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-20T04:33:17.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20201120/6H37QHA72FGHBNRPUPSYM6D7WA/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20201120%2F6H37QHA72FGHBNRPUPSYM6D7WA%2F&d=gxBKi3yaaNwv0eARaXv6BRTmJET03dBbukdTSFliYCA%3D&h=32e715f7\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20201120%2F6H37QHA72FGHBNRPUPSYM6D7WA%2F&h=f13ce4b9\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20201120/6H37QHA72FGHBNRPUPSYM6D7WA/</a><br />\n<br />\n節錄<br />\n<br />\n周梓樂案 新聞片顯示有煙冒出 <br />\n首認射TG入車場 警：不見煙<br />\n<br />\n【死因研訊】<br />\n<br />\n相關新聞：行動無對錶 官：紀錄明顯不準<br />\n<br />\n【本報訊】科大男生周梓樂去年11月4日凌晨在尚德邨停車場墮樓昏迷，留醫五天不治，終年22歲。死因庭昨續研訊，新聞片段拍到梓樂墮樓前十分鐘內至少兩次有濃煙在2至3樓出現，但多名警員均稱不見有煙飄出。昨首度有防暴警承認所發射的催淚彈落入2樓，即與梓樂倒卧的同一層；梓樂被發現前的半小時中，昨日作供的三名警員已向停車場內外發射至少15枚催淚彈；指揮官同一個指令更有機會導致多於一名防暴警向相同位置發射。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/Rvrsy1Aav6uh7Cm9go17COmGZcI=/640x460/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/BL4OVFM7OFGR7GHL3NQU43VRSQ.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FRvrsy1Aav6uh7Cm9go17COmGZcI%3D%2F640x460%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FBL4OVFM7OFGR7GHL3NQU43VRSQ.jpg&h=c81758e8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n■梓樂墮樓前，有新聞片段顯示停車場樓層內冒出催淚煙。<br />\n<br />\n依照早前證供，。。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n警方衝鋒隊第4小隊女警楊樂欣昨繼續作供，。。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/eAcYRS-KKK2m8heLkYGNSjyQVMQ=/640x350/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/QTS5QLM4DREWHOWNAQWLN5R6EQ.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FeAcYRS-KKK2m8heLkYGNSjyQVMQ%3D%2F640x350%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FQTS5QLM4DREWHOWNAQWLN5R6EQ.jpg&h=16bbff4a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n■警方當日向停車場發射催淚彈。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/AlPKeUXdwbEJJ9Tvw4d5jGDjoTU=/640x700/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/HHQ5ZK3DKVF5LLHDDZPX4RQURU.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FAlPKeUXdwbEJJ9Tvw4d5jGDjoTU%3D%2F640x700%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FHHQ5ZK3DKVF5LLHDDZPX4RQURU.jpg&h=04bf9cbd&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n■女警楊樂欣昨估計所發射的催淚彈落入2樓，即梓樂倒卧的同一層。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/7Lb2sZumZ6mslJui3FyTEQCdo40=/640x800/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/QXNMCU6JYVEHLEFKP6X6OCPIAM.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2F7Lb2sZumZ6mslJui3FyTEQCdo40%3D%2F640x800%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FQXNMCU6JYVEHLEFKP6X6OCPIAM.jpg&h=d405db9e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n警員嚴卓勳<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n或多於一人向相同位置發射<br />\n<br />\n同隊警員嚴卓勳供稱，零時44分至56分按指揮官指示，先後向唐俊街築傘陣及擲物的「暴徒」發射五枚催淚彈，他忘記彈芯確實落點，但估計均落在傘陣前。1時09分，十多名示威者在停車場2樓向警方投擲雪糕筒等硬物，他再按指揮官指示，向2樓發射一枚催淚彈。他稱目睹該枚彈芯進入了停車場2樓，原本在該處的示威者隨即散開，但他看不見彈芯落點飄出煙霧。<br />\n<br />\n研訊主任播放當晚直播片段，。。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n家屬一方大律師鄭淑儀盤問時，。。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n同隊警員方震國供稱，。。。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n法庭昨早休後，。。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n案件編號：CCDI932/19<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/1tMPJzoAN7rLN80WDzweJXw4Jqk=/882x215/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/E3BIGWQBORFOJHD2KQ6F6N5GU4.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2F1tMPJzoAN7rLN80WDzweJXw4Jqk%3D%2F882x215%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FE3BIGWQBORFOJHD2KQ6F6N5GU4.jpg&h=8f16dbe5&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"d8914927ccc4637dc68af77a08c12334ed0c9c1e","tid":2293112,"uid":323740,"like":1,"dislike":32,"score":-31,"citedBy":7,"replyTime":"2020-11-20T04:43:50.000Z","msg":"有煙=TG<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />可能有其他人食緊萬寶路<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5957c0a1c6692da0afd99d884177a0816e74f85f","tid":2293112,"uid":55597,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"d8914927ccc4637dc68af77a08c12334ed0c9c1e","tid":2293112,"uid":323740,"like":1,"dislike":32,"score":-31,"citedBy":7,"replyTime":"2020-11-20T04:43:50.000Z","msg":"有煙=TG<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />可能有其他人食緊萬寶路<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-20T04:47:54.000Z","msg":"一次過點幾多支萬寶路先有咁大煙？"},{"pid":"63a444c6c2d55f4549370e29eb0a18391b8a2a6e","tid":2293112,"uid":66392,"like":9,"dislike":1,"score":8,"quote":{"pid":"d8914927ccc4637dc68af77a08c12334ed0c9c1e","tid":2293112,"uid":323740,"like":1,"dislike":32,"score":-31,"citedBy":7,"replyTime":"2020-11-20T04:43:50.000Z","msg":"有煙=TG<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />可能有其他人食緊萬寶路<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-20T04:51:31.000Z","msg":"咪撚以為自己好撚幽默啦 定係其實你係黑警/五毛狗想幫佢哋兜呀弱智"},{"pid":"46f99629585f467dde639d27395a467cfe564a66","tid":2293112,"uid":143151,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"5957c0a1c6692da0afd99d884177a0816e74f85f","tid":2293112,"uid":55597,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"d8914927ccc4637dc68af77a08c12334ed0c9c1e","tid":2293112,"uid":323740,"like":1,"dislike":32,"score":-31,"cit